data.description: *Short Sale subject to lienholder approval. Nestled in Wordsworth Village w/ pretty lawn views this largest 2nd floor condo features 1-level living & is elevator compatible w/ shaft/phone line/power source. Lightly lived in 2nd home for many years. Foyer w/ ceramic tile flooring & brand-new carpeting. Cozy great room w/ fireplace, entertainment cabinet, & adjoining formal dining room. Bright kitchen features a breakfast nook, oak raised panel cabinets, & utility closet w/ washer & dryer. The primary suite features a HUGE closet, & sitting room. The ensuite bath has a white double vanity w/ new top, a separate shower w/ glass enclosure, a jetted tub w/ hand shower & white tile surround. Step outside to the covered porch, complete with a composite deck & retractable screen–perfect for enjoying the outdoors. Additional updates include Trane A/C, range & refrigerator (all 2016). Come experience condo living in this vibrant 55+ community w/ clubhouse, activities, fitness center & pool.
